{"id":60653,"title":"Systemic vasculitis: an annual critical digest of the most recent literature.","abstract":"Herewith we provide our annual digest of the recent literature on systemic vasculitis in which we reviewed all the articles published during the last 12 months on large-, medium- and small-vessel vasculitis, and selected the most relevant studies regarding the epidemiology, pathogenesis and management of systemic vasculitis. In particular, we focused the attention on giant cell arteritis, ANCA-associated vasculitis and cryoglobulinaemia. ","date":"2014-05-23","categories":"Hemic and Lymphatic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24854379","annotations":[{"name":"Epidemiology","weight":0.689429,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Epidemiology"},{"name":"Vasculitis","weight":0.252918,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vasculitis"},{"name":"Digestion","weight":0.143824,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digestion"},{"name":"Literature","weight":0.125424,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Literature"},{"name":"Cell (biology)","weight":0.0805305,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cell_(biology)"},{"name":"Giant cell arteritis","weight":0.0342852,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Giant_cell_arteritis"},{"name":"Cryoglobulinemia","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cryoglobulinemia"},{"name":"Pathogenesis","weight":0.0274275,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pathogenesis"},{"name":"Giant star","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Giant_star"},{"name":"Arteritis","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arteritis"},{"name":"Systemic disease","weight":0.0168322,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Systemic_disease"},{"name":"Annual plant","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Annual_plant"},{"nam